"No pill is safe", but just how dangerous is #MDMA? The safety ratio of MDMA is 16. This compares to alcohol which has safety ratio of 10 and paracetamol that has safety ratio of 5.
 This means that MDMA is at least three times safer than paracetamol. In fact when it comes to MDMA by far the biggest single factor in determining potential to cause death is environment.